title: Arnette Surf Crew Slays The North Shore
description:
Arnette's Hawaiian surf brigade recently linked up for a serious shred session at The North Shore. Check out Fred Patacchia, Joel Centeio, Mason Ho, Timmy Reyes and Zeke Lau doing what they do best!

Find out what the rest of the Arnette team is up to at: http://www.arnette.com/
